TestNG (New Generation) 
	1. unit testing framework
	2. supports TDD (Test Driven Development)
	3. its a open source tool, available in the form of jar
	4. used for java based unit testing frameworks
	
Purpose:
	1. design test cases in systematic way
	2. provides html test execution reports
	3. different annotations
	4. proirities/sequence
	5. attach dependency with other tests
	6. provides grouping concept
	7. has data provider feature to execute same test case (Login) with multiple inputs
	
Install:
	1. point to "http://beust.com/eclipse/" in the eclipse and install
	2. Add the  testNG lib to the build path
	
	